{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-project-template-tsx","path":"/project/solniverse/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h1>개요</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>자율 프로젝트 : 공통, 특화 프로젝트 경험을 바탕으로 자유 주제로 서비스 개발</p>\n<p>기업연계/오픈소스/자유주제 중 택 1 ➝ 기업연계 선택</p>\n<p>7개 기업 중 선택 ➝ 메인메타(GetPIP.com 서비스를 제공하는 블록체인 기술기반의 스타트업)</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>인터넷 방송 플랫폼에서 방송하는 크리에이터와 크리에이터에게 후원하는 시청자가 간편하게 Solana pay로 결제하고 후원 내역을 관리하며 다양한 Gamification 기능을 이용할 수 있는 서비스</p>\n<h1>아키텍처</h1>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a070775e76dc2669cc145489a3c883f8/cdba3/architecture.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47.39583333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/a070775e76dc2669cc145489a3c883f8/a59e9/architecture.webp 192w,\n/static/a070775e76dc2669cc145489a3c883f8/0ca9f/architecture.webp 384w,\n/static/a070775e76dc2669cc145489a3c883f8/dc9b9/architecture.webp 768w,\n/static/a070775e76dc2669cc145489a3c883f8/e2c2f/architecture.webp 1152w,\n/static/a070775e76dc2669cc145489a3c883f8/f3efb/architecture.webp 1536w,\n/static/a070775e76dc2669cc145489a3c883f8/3c9f0/architecture.webp 5558w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/a070775e76dc2669cc145489a3c883f8/3b721/architecture.png 192w,\n/static/a070775e76dc2669cc145489a3c883f8/66595/architecture.png 384w,\n/static/a070775e76dc2669cc145489a3c883f8/fe486/architecture.png 768w,\n/static/a070775e76dc2669cc145489a3c883f8/d2d74/architecture.png 1152w,\n/static/a070775e76dc2669cc145489a3c883f8/e8464/architecture.png 1536w,\n/static/a070775e76dc2669cc145489a3c883f8/cdba3/architecture.png 5558w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/a070775e76dc2669cc145489a3c883f8/fe486/architecture.png\"\n            alt=\"architecture\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h1>담당 개발 내용</h1>\n<h2>프로젝트 세팅</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>CRA를 통한 React 프로젝트 생성 (TypeScript)</li>\n<li>초기 라이브러리 설치</li>\n<li>폴더 구조</li>\n<li>Global style &#x26; Theme light/dark</li>\n<li>반응형 Layout</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">recoil</code>을 통한 상태관리 (<code class=\"language-text\">recoil-persist</code>를 통한 로컬 스토리지 활용)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>디자인 및 퍼블리싱</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Navbar &#x26; Sidebar</li>\n<li>메인 페이지\n<ul>\n<li>대시보드</li>\n<li>등급표</li>\n<li>순위표</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>후원 내역 페이지\n<ul>\n<li>후원한 내역</li>\n<li>후원받은 내역</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>계정 페이지\n<ul>\n<li>계정 상세</li>\n<li>후원 설정</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>기능</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>메인 대시보드 및 순위 조회</li>\n<li>후원 내역 <code class=\"language-text\">Apexcharts.js</code>\n<ul>\n<li>사용자 지갑 주소로 후원한/후원받은 모든 트랜잭션을 백엔드에서 받아옴</li>\n<li>받아온 트랜잭션을 SOL 또는 USDC에 따라 분기</li>\n<li>분기된 코인을 Object에 날짜별로 합산</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Twitch OAuth\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://dev.twitch.tv/docs/authentication/getting-tokens-oauth/#authorization-code-grant-flow\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Authorization code grant flow</a> 적용</li>\n<li>URI에 client_id, redirect_uri 담아 요청</li>\n<li>사용자가 로그인 시 redirect_uri로 보내지면 query parameter에서 code를 받아옴</li>\n<li>useEffect를 활용하여 code 가져왔을 때 백엔드에 code 전송</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Phantom wallet에서 SOL 및 USDC의 잔액과 SNV 토큰 개수 조회 <code class=\"language-text\">solana/web3</code></li>\n<li>다국어 기능 <code class=\"language-text\">i18next</code>\n<ul>\n<li>적용할 텍스트를 json 파일에 key 값과 함께 정의</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>산출물</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/wonjongjang/PJT-Solniverse-v2/blob/master/frontend/src/components/Layout.tsx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">반응형 Layout 및 Header</a>\n<img src=\"/d7925b04507eafcca5e6c6361160c744/layout.gif\" alt=\"layout\"></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/wonjongjang/PJT-Solniverse-v2/blob/master/frontend/src/pages/my-info/Main.tsx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">메인 페이지</a>\n<img src=\"/408431df28e01ce2688add3f56eca499/main.gif\" alt=\"main\"></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/wonjongjang/PJT-Solniverse-v2/blob/master/frontend/src/pages/my-info/DonationHistory.tsx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">후원 내역</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/wonjongjang/PJT-Solniverse-v2/blob/master/frontend/src/components/DonationHistory/Send.tsx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">후원한 내역</a>\n<img src=\"/c210985158e23fae6676d85392f6195b/send.gif\" alt=\"send\"></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/wonjongjang/PJT-Solniverse-v2/blob/master/frontend/src/components/DonationHistory/Receive.tsx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">후원받은 내역</a>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 51.5625%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/48169a1c8307ec2713346689f16b848d/a59e9/receive.webp 192w,\n/static/48169a1c8307ec2713346689f16b848d/0ca9f/receive.webp 384w,\n/static/48169a1c8307ec2713346689f16b848d/dc9b9/receive.webp 768w,\n/static/48169a1c8307ec2713346689f16b848d/e2c2f/receive.webp 1152w,\n/static/48169a1c8307ec2713346689f16b848d/f3efb/receive.webp 1536w,\n/static/48169a1c8307ec2713346689f16b848d/53e68/receive.webp 1843w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/48169a1c8307ec2713346689f16b848d/150b2/receive.jpg 192w,\n/static/48169a1c8307ec2713346689f16b848d/6985d/receive.jpg 384w,\n/static/48169a1c8307ec2713346689f16b848d/19de6/receive.jpg 768w,\n/static/48169a1c8307ec2713346689f16b848d/4472f/receive.jpg 1152w,\n/static/48169a1c8307ec2713346689f16b848d/d58d1/receive.jpg 1536w,\n/static/48169a1c8307ec2713346689f16b848d/1adca/receive.jpg 1843w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/48169a1c8307ec2713346689f16b848d/19de6/receive.jpg\"\n            alt=\"receive\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/wonjongjang/PJT-Solniverse-v2/blob/master/frontend/src/components/Settings/Account.tsx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">계정 상세</a>\n<img src=\"/55583d1329ce419e823bfd03289e91b0/account.gif\" alt=\"account\"></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/wonjongjang/PJT-Solniverse-v2/blob/master/frontend/src/components/Settings/Donation.tsx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">후원 설정</a>\n<img src=\"/3666e165b90a718f15f344f2c9c194f6/donation-setting.gif\" alt=\"donation-setting\"></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/wonjongjang/PJT-Solniverse-v2/blob/master/frontend/src/styles/theme.ts\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Theme light/dark</a>\n<img src=\"/d81c71863b3ac266800de41b241e2dcf/theme.gif\" alt=\"theme\"></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/wonjongjang/PJT-Solniverse-v2/blob/master/frontend/src/locales/i18n.ts\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">다국어</a>\n<img src=\"/4f9792743370a31f33dd313b5dc74e66/language.gif\" alt=\"language\"></li>\n</ul>\n<h1>성과</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>온라인 반별 발표회 후, 반별 상위 2개 팀에 선정 (전국 14개 반, 100여 개 팀 중 28개 팀) ➝ 온라인 전국 발표회 진출</li>\n<li>온라인 전국 발표회 후, 상위 8개 팀에 선정 ➝ 오프라인 결선 발표회 진출</li>\n<li>기업연계반 베스트 팀 2회 선정</li>\n<li>우수상 - 자율 프로젝트 기업연계반 7팀 중 1위</li>\n<li>우수상 - 자율 프로젝트 결선발표회 입상</li>\n<li>UCC 우수상 - 자율 프로젝트 UCC 전체 2위</li>\n<li>프로젝트 종료 후에도 메인메타와 지속적인 협업 ➝ 솔라나 해커톤 및 해커하우스 참가</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"page":"project","startDate":"2022.04.11","endDate":"2022.05.27","title":"Solniverse","subTitle":"Solana 블록체인을 활용한 인터넷 방송 서드파티 후원 플랫폼","categories":["React","TypeScript","Styled-components","Solana/web3","Git","Jira"],"team":["프론트엔드2","백엔드2","블록체인1","데이터분석1"],"link":["","https://github.com/wonjongjang/PJT-Solniverse-v2"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/181f8110025f972225e8d05a6f5e1006/839ae/ssafy.jpg","srcSet":"/static/181f8110025f972225e8d05a6f5e1006/2fed4/ssafy.jpg 50w,\n/static/181f8110025f972225e8d05a6f5e1006/93e3f/ssafy.jpg 100w,\n/static/181f8110025f972225e8d05a6f5e1006/839ae/ssafy.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 200px) 200px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/181f8110025f972225e8d05a6f5e1006/9afd2/ssafy.webp 50w,\n/static/181f8110025f972225e8d05a6f5e1006/e64f1/ssafy.webp 100w,\n/static/181f8110025f972225e8d05a6f5e1006/8b00d/ssafy.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 200px) 200px, 100vw"}]},"width":200,"height":200}}}}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/project/solniverse/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}